'''Gyanjyoti Higher Secondary School''', situated at Rajgadh is a school of Jhapa district located south-east of the headquarters [[Chandragadhi]].<ref>[http://www.educationinnepal.com/directory_by_boards.php?view=insts&bid=5 Institutions By Boards In Nepal]</ref> Established in 1994 (2051 [[Vikram Samvat|BS]]), it is providing quality [[education]] to the students. Initially started as primary level at Mr. Narayan Dhakal's house (former Principal) in 1949 BS, it has got its registration since 2051 BS. Later in 2057 BS, it produced the first S.L.C. Batch.
